column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/4d7a1619bc4b5c8b042ca80b0980e1d5c5d4532b for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

Please make the translation changes in transifex (https://www.transifex.com/projects/p/bitcoin/) - they are pulled from there before releases.

The image optimizations are fine, but can you do them in one commit?
Translation changes are now on transifex. I will do one commit for the image optimizations. Thanks\n
